Review: Obi-Wan Kenobi's Jedi Starfighter - SW [S - P1] - KB Toys Exclusive 
Posted by | April 16, 2017 at 12:02 AM ET 
It is time to check out Obi-Wan Kenobi's Jedi Starfighter (again), but this time as a KB Toys exclusive. This one came with a pack-in figure. And it's also part of the Star Wars "Saga" lineup. It's the focus of our Research Droids Reviews today. Be sure to leave your own thoughts in our comments section, vote in the poll or even leave comments about it on our Facebook page. Click the banner below for the direct link to the review! As always, you can also send your own personal review requests via if you'd like to see something that we didn't cover yet..
